<i>"I will gladly pay you Tuesday for Sushi today!"</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 450<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/7/02 12:34:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2252.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AC soft cap and such?</span><hr size=1> As a ranger I can tell you that there is a big difference between low 800's-mid 800's and breaking 900.  Havent managed to break 1000 except with other people's buffs, but it seems a small increase.<br>
